-- Brookfield Properties Plans to Become a Pure-Play Office Property Firm
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-07-30T11:02:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/brookfield-properties-plans-to-become-a-pure-play-office-property-firm.html

          
          
             Brookfield Properties Corp.
disclosed a plan to change to a “pure-play office property
company.”  
 The plan includes the acquisition of an interest in a
portfolio of premier office properties in Australia from
Brookfield Asset Management and the divestment of Brookfield
Properties’ residential land and housing business.   
          
          


  


        